TunableList.name: relationship
TunableList.description:
List specifying a series of relationship(s) to recursively traverse to find the desired target sim. i.e. to find "cousins", we get all the "parents". And then we get "aunts/uncles" by getting the "siblings" of those "parents". And then we finally get the "cousins" by getting the "children" of those "aunts/uncles".
So: Set of "parent" bitflag(s) Set of "sibling" bitflag(s) Set of "children" bitflag(s)
Can also find direct existing relationships by only having a single entry in the list.
Set of relbits to use for this relationship.
